        "logic": "var calc_output = [];\nvar age = parseFloat(age);\nvar pre = parseFloat(pre)/100;\n if (UOMSYSTEM == true) {\nvar bnp = bnp;\n}if (UOMSYSTEM == false) {\n  var bnp = bnp/0.1182;\n}\n\nvar y = 8 + (0.011*age) - (5.9*pre) - (2.3*Math.log10(bnp)) + (0.82*pre*(Math.log10(bnp)));\nvar ahf = (1 / (1 + Math.exp(y)))*100;\n\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'mini',\n    value: ahf.toFixed(0),\n    value_text: '%',\n    message: 'Probability of clinical AHF diagnosis'\n});\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'ahf',\n    value: ahf.toFixed(0),\n    value_text: '%',\n    message: 'Probability of clinical AHF diagnosis'\n});",
